{"tid":1401281,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議]關於罷買！！！","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T00:15:52.000Z","uid":25169,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b2071b23c66ddafd2d5143e940b3ac850c8832c1","tid":1401281,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"(一) 香港人消費<br />\n大致上可分為兩大類<br />\n(a)  必須品(衣食住行)<br />\n(b)  非必須品(零食，奢侈品,etc.)<br />\n就非必須品而言，如果罷買當然希望大家買少d。但必須品唯一可以減少消費嘅，應該主要係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食</span></strong>呢一方面，而睇返數字，好多人生活開支都喺食呢一方面<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp290_tc.jsp?tableID=54D&amp;ID=0&amp;productType=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Fsub%2Fsp290_tc.jsp%3FtableID%3D54D%26ID%3D0%26productType%3D8&d=DXsCe6mrroMB06wP0eqGVUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=a8ddaa26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp290_tc.jsp?tableID=54D&amp;ID=0&amp;productType=8</a><br />\n睇返數字，其實香港人外出用膳消費係好多<br />\n<br />\n(二) 計劃<br />\n簡單d講，其實係整d簡易食譜/無火食譜俾大家用。<br />\n(1)  整Google form：識煮野嘅巴絲俾建議，或者大家上網揾下資料，集思廣益。<br />\n(2)  整合資料：可能要整個飲食小隊group。<br />\n(3)  宣傳：整個channel，po相拍片咁。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個channel出街之後share俾老母。不論立場，有得慳錢又唔洗諗煮咩，變相佢都參與罷買。</span><br />\n<br />\n(三) 其他建議/優點<br />\n(1) 買d麥皮做早餐，幾十蚊食好耐，又有益。<br />\n(2) 避免一窩蜂衝去食d&quot;良心企業&quot;，跟住集體炒車。<br />\n(3) 和理非都可以參與。<br />\n(4) 可以開其他po，討論點樣減低其他方面消費。<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得可行，請正皮幫推"},{"pid":"f2024ad0368273b31bcea85ab51f2a09aa7b8550","tid":1401281,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e409462f734ac0d334fd37fe963c339874cbaaf","tid":1401281,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d35e5251afe8f49335ea777c85a273acd87dfd",